.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.local
.env
# NOTE: `.claude/*` (not `.claude/`) is deliberate — a bare directory
# exclude blocks git from descending into it at all, which makes the
# negation carve-out below a no-op (a known git gitignore limitation:
# you cannot re-include paths under an excluded *directory*, only under
# excluded *contents*). `.claude/*` ignores the same set of top-level
# entries but still lets negated sub-patterns re-include specific paths.
.claude/*
.worktrees/

# Repo-local dev agent (NEVER packaged/shipped — see g-dev/README.md and
# .claude/agents/g-forge-dev.md's own header). Everything else under
# .claude/ stays ignored (it's this machine's installed copy of the
# plugin dogfooding itself); this is the sole carve-out.
!.claude/agents/
.claude/agents/*
!.claude/agents/g-forge-dev.md

# G-Forge operational artifacts — regenerable, not project record (not plugin content).
# Tracking now lives under g-docs/ and IS committed (g-docs/ROADMAP.md, g-docs/todo.md,
# g-docs/todo-done.md, g-docs/milestones/, decisions/, retros/, …). Only the regenerable
# raw-output paths below are ignored.
/CLAUDE.md
g-docs/plans/
g-docs/agent-output/
g-docs/superpowers/
